- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with inferring properties of concepts using machine learning techniques.
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper deals with contextual usage of concepts in textual data.
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper may involve discussions on the computational complexity of the proposed approach.
